reviews.headline: Hydration, Brightening and Firming all in one
reviews.comments: L'Oreal Paris Triple Power Face and Neck SPF 30 is a decent, affordable everyday moisturizer with SPF 30. It hydrates well and is readily available. However, it can feel heavy, has a noticeable fragrance, and doesn't produce dramatic anti-aging results. Best for normal to dry skin, it's a good option if you prioritize affordability and sun protection.  If you have oily or sensitive skin, or dislike fragrance, consider other options.

reviews.headline: I would probably use more as a summertime SPF.
reviews.comments: L'Oreal Paris Revitalift Triple Power Face and Neck Moisturizer SPF 30 with Pro-Retinol, Vitamin C & Hyaluronic acid is perfectly packaged. With its thick moisturizing consistency I'd say it's a little thicker than anticipated and took some getting used to. Also, I'm an extremely sensitive skinned person that breaks out easily with some scents & comedogenic products. After several weeks of usage I did feel it smoothed my neck, however I did experience some breakouts on my face. I would probably use this product as more of a summertime SPF than a daily moisturizing cream.

reviews.headline: luxury
reviews.comments: 'LOreal Paris Revitalift Triple Power Anti-Aging Face Moisturizer, Pro Retinol, Hyaluronic Acid & Vitamin C to Reduce Wrinkles, Firm & Brighten Skin really does what it claims and MORE! I use this in the morning after I wash my face, but before applying my foundation for the day. It's an integral part of my routine to also use this in the evening after I remove my makekup for the day, but before bed. This leaves my skin hydrated yet moisturized, but also acts as a solid base for my foundation making it not only stretch farther but also moisturizing my skin and helping with fine lines and wrinkles that come with aging. I LOVE the versatility of this product and its light scent. This is one of my most favorite staples and I highly recommend L'Oreal Paris Revitalift Triple Power Anti-Aging Face Moisturizer, Pro Retinol, Hyaluronic Acid & Vitamin C to Reduce Wrinkles, Firm & Brighten Skin. Give it a try, I think you'll love it.

reviews.headline: Great for day and night cream
reviews.comments: Don't be fooled by the little jar, this cream packs a lot of punch. One of the best things about it, is that it pulls double duty as a day cream with the SPF and night cream. Using it at night gives the skin that little bit of extra moisture needed for night time. I can definitely see a difference in my skin after using this for almost a month.  I was given this product in exchange for an honest review

reviews.headline: Keeping This As A Must!!
reviews.comments: Such a perfect day cream! I received this product about a month ago and have been consistently using it day and night. Even in the winter, I can go all day and night with my skin not only feeling baby smooth soft, and not greasy or shiny. When putting it on, I was struck by the thickness of the cream, yet it slides on easily and just melts into the skin. I am so happy it has spf 30, so I feel confident using it during the daytime. It doesn't roll on the skin, and also does not make my makeup slip off. I could barely smell a scent, and it just lifts up the face and gives it a nice, subtle glow. I also noticed a marked improvement in the texture on my neck. Love it!!

reviews.headline: Yes!
reviews.comments: I received This free in exchange for my honest review. This one now replace my much more expensive lotion. It has wonderful ingredients and left my skin feeling so smooth. Blurred my lines and pores. I love the scent of this. I will definitely be repurchasing this. Works much better than the more expensive brand.

reviews.headline: Love this product
reviews.comments: Goes on smooth and evenly. I've used this product every day since I received it. It helps moisturize my face, while lifting in just the right places.

reviews.headline: Part of my routine for life!
reviews.comments: There will never not be a day where I don't use this cream. It is like heaven on your face!

reviews.headline: I buy again
reviews.comments: I have never tried loreal skincare products before ... .....but I can say that this cream has become one of my favorites to daily use .....I  use it in the mornings and my skin looks radiant 100% super recomended

reviews.headline: Beautiful firmer skin
reviews.comments: This stuff is amazing, it makes my skin soft, plump and hydrated. It goes on smooth and absorbs really well. I've only been using it a few weeks and my skin's appearance has already improved, looking forward to seeing how well it works on my neck with continued use. I am almost 50, so keeping my skin hydrated and firmer looking is getting harder to do, this product has helped.

reviews.headline: Great moisturizer
reviews.comments: L'Oréal has been one of my favorite brands for skincare. Love that they are now including sunscreen. It's so important and is not included already with my moisturizer. It's such lightweight and provides the care my skin needs. Has a pleasant scent not overbearing at all. Has a smooth texture.

reviews.headline: Wonderful product, works great
reviews.comments: This moisturizer is a great product.  It has SPF unblocking as well as being non-greasy.  I used it every night and it made my skin feel alive and hearty.  After a few uses, the fine lines around my eyes were gone.

reviews.headline: Hydrating, smoothing and wonderful
reviews.comments: Use this to keep your skin on point . It moisturized making my skin look flawless . It was fragrance free ,great for sensitive skin. Would definitely tell my friends.

reviews.headline: It's ok
reviews.comments: This seems like another fairly good face cream. I wish they would become more naturally based, but it is what it is. It's creamy and smooths on well, leaving skin feeling soft.

reviews.headline: yes yes yes
reviews.comments: Omg had to use this immediately and it's so good! The smell is great and my skin is so so so soft. It's Definitely effective and the packaging I absolutely love. I also like that I can understand the ingredients and it doesn't smell like chemical.

reviews.headline: Super hydrating and feels great!
reviews.comments: This does have a slight fragrance. It's ok with me but it is not fragrance me because the scent is very light and dissipates quickly. It is very hydrating and makes my skin feel good. As thick as it is, itt absorbs very fast. I do wish that it left a bit more of a glow on my skin.

reviews.headline: Anti aging cream
reviews.comments: This is an anti aging cream with added sunscreen. I love having both in one to give the added protection. It goes on smooth and keeps your skin feeling refreshed. It works well under makeup during the day. I like a bit thicker lotion for nighttime, but overall this one works well too. I would use this more during the day since it has the sunscreen, rather than overnight.

reviews.headline: I love this product!
reviews.comments: Love the jar and smells amazing. Spf 30 is great for the skin. The product absorbs really well into the skin and so far is working really well to hydrate. I love how my skin looks after applying! This is a staple in your everyday routine.

faceoff_positive.comments: I have started using this for one week and I already see a big difference in my skin. It goes on smooth and silky and sinks in. My color is better, my skin more supple, and my spots are fading. And yes, My wrinkles are less prominent. I have tried so many creams (Including #7) and nothing did what they said. This is the first time I am totally satisfied with a skin care product. It does what it says. It does not get "pilly" when you put on makeup like so many of the face creams do. I am 65 and so happy I took a leap of faith and purchased this product. I always use L'Oreal hair products and hair dye so it made sense to try this. I LOVE THIS!!
faceoff_positive.headline: It WORKS!!!

faceoff_negative.comments: I received this about a month ago. It is a very thick consistency which I like when I very dehydrated. I use it at night and in the morning my skin feels plump and hyrdrated. I'm really enjoying it.
